<p style="text-align:center;max-width:800px;margin:auto;">
Aayan Color Craft is a trusted supplier of high-quality paints and protective chemical solutions.
We provide durable, vibrant, and long-lasting finishes for homes and commercial spaces.
</p>
</section>

