<div class="card"><h3>Exterior Paints</h3><p>Weather-resistant protection.</p></div>
<div class="card"><h3>Protective Coatings</h3><p>Waterproof & durable coatings.</p></div>
<div class="card"><h3>Consultation</h3><p>Expert color advice.</p></div>
</div>
</section>

<section id="gallery" class="section">
